# Project: awesome-openclaw (Astro + Starlight)
# Goal: SEO-optimized Chinese tutorial site for "ai openclaw" with a custom homepage

## Tech Stack
- Framework: Astro + @astrojs/starlight
- Styling: Tailwind + custom CSS in `src/styles/custom.css`
- Pages: `src/pages/index.astro` (custom landing), docs in `src/content/docs/*`

## Conventions
- Use `rg` for search. Prefer `apply_patch` for edits.
- Avoid Python for file edits; use shell or Node if needed.
- Keep typography and layout consistent with existing hero/home styles.
- Do not remove the hero design or replace its structure unless explicitly asked.

## SEO Requirements
- Meta Title length: 40-60 characters per page.
- Meta Description length: 140-160 characters per page.
- Each page has exactly one `# H1` and a logical H2/H3 hierarchy.
- Canonical URLs must be set to `https://aiopenclaw.app/<path>/` (always trailing slash).
- Add social meta tags on all pages:
  - `og:title`, `og:url`, `og:description`, `og:image` (use site icon)

## Reusable Layout
- Global header/footer are provided by `src/components/SiteHeader.astro` and `src/components/SiteFooter.astro`.
- Starlight header/footer are overridden via `astro.config.mjs`.
- When editing navigation/footer links, update the shared components, not individual pages.

## Images
- Store site images in `public/images/`.
- For decorative assets, prefer lightweight JPG and set `loading="lazy"`.

## Content
- Keep content in Chinese, clear and instructional.
- Maintain keyword focus on "ai openclaw" without stuffing.
- If adding new pages, update sidebar in `astro.config.mjs`.
